Approach 1

class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfFour(int n) {
        if(n <= 0) return false;

        while(n > 0 && n%4 == 0) {
            n = n / 4;
        }

        if(n == 1) return true;
        else return false;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(log n)
Space Complexity : O(1)

Approach 2

class Solution {
    public boolean isPowerOfFour(int n) {
        if(n <= 0) return false;
        if((n & n-1) == 0 && Integer.bitCount(n-1) % 2 == 0) return true;
        return false;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(1)
Space Complexity : O(1)
